{"tid":1350102,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武手足同我入晒嚟2.0！！！","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T11:51:04.000Z","uid":207904,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dccbbf6781cd0a396f15c71953f0e02fbb0d2d9a","tid":1350102,"uid":207904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:57:53.000Z","msg":"各位勇武手足我喺度同大家講句對唔住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我上一個post講話盡量唔好打死班狗最好用索帶綁撚住班狗，當初咁講係我太天真，我喺度道歉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鑑於而家班警犬嘅武力一次俾一次高，我哋勇武手足都要無底線咁提升武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論前線點樣升級武力我都會堅定繼續支持大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以小弟嘅愚見，班元朗鄉黑個個爛命一條，打交最怕係見到一個唔怕死嘅，所以我哋要比佢更加凶狠。屌晒佢哋老母，琴晚發夢喺上環返咗屋企之後，睇住元朗個直播真係嬲撚到我仆街，屌佢老母，大肚婆、記者同路人係人就打，屌佢老母如果我哋今次唔撚報仇點吞得落呢啖氣。<br />\n<br />\n除咗應付班鄉黑，要諗下點樣對付下班狗，我哋去元朗覆卓嘅時候班狗實唔會搞啲鄉黑，仲會搞9返我哋，到時就變咗開兩條戰線，各位手足有咩高見提出，我哋大家討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺武力升級方面，琴日上環嗰度真係比714沙田嗰陣進步咗唔少，亦多咗唔少兵種，攻擊方式亦冇以前咁單調，各位繼續加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"2d03bed39d900f3d06b1c30ed46a180db085a7f5","tid":1350102,"uid":207904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:58:07.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1911da82de427f090ab30622254ca5088d2f7b55","tid":1350102,"uid":207904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"各位新界區嘅手足，呢幾日都要小心啲，雖然有好多消息都未fact check ，但寧可信其有，留返條命仔先可以繼續抗爭，一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0676b02744413b74275a3db8f14faf2957483db","tid":1350102,"uid":207904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d782c5a2f52dcce2c2131b1842b2332638cfdf","tid":1350102,"uid":207904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94178b740dc303e8864e734c97105360483e6887","tid":1350102,"uid":263555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:01:13.000Z","msg":"我好撚多野想講但冇野講"},{"pid":"2724fb816ba2c2f37a5737ca6b3fd9f40ea8d565","tid":1350102,"uid":207904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:01:21.000Z","msg":"推 屌佢老母一定要覆卓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f442434aa8ec5fe68e4a1569a23f28f40a31a76","tid":1350102,"uid":207904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:02:02.000Z","msg":"你老母何妖死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f07374143c5646326b9863284c4f6e1fe10a46","tid":1350102,"uid":207904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94178b740dc303e8864e734c97105360483e6887",